<< WOW!! REally fabulous job Sandra...I am impressed.

That's Holly's calling. I was just the technician.
I'm a grunt.
Holly says "chop here, shave here," I whimper and then cut.
Keith says "remove stick" I whimper and cut.

Rough week for me, who thinks hair should just be left to grow in peace and
women shouldn't cut their husbands with knives unless they're REALLY tired of
them.

Sandra
